#

Dal Bukhara

$15.99
450 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

Indian CuisineComfort FoodSlow Cook

Description

A rich and creamy black lentil dish slow-cooked to perfection, offering a delightful blend of spices and textures.

Ingredients

  • Black lentils (urad dal): 1 cup
  • Tomatoes: 2 large, pureed
  • Onion: 1 large, finely chopped
  • Ginger-garlic paste: 1 tablespoon
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Cream: 1/4 cup
  • Cumin seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • Garam masala: 1 teaspoon
  • Turmeric powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Red chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Cilantro leaves: for garnish
